      <title>О вдохновении и мракобесии</title>
      <link>http://shinmem.org/%D0%BE-%D0%B2%D0%B4%D0%BE%D1%85%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B8-%D0%B8-%D0%BC%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%B8%D0%B8/</link>
